比夏爾","Europe":"艾歐洛","Salisbury, Wiltshire, England":"英國維爾爾索爾茲伯里","lifeSummary":"當Mathilda de Derbyshire於1050年出生在英國德比夏爾時，她的父親William F. de Derbyshire31歲，母親Lady P De Normandie15歲。她於大約1063年與Ranulph Fitz-Hubert de Rie在法國諾門迪卡爾瓦多斯法拉結婚。他們至少是1個兒子和2個女兒的父母。她去世在英國維爾爾索爾茲伯里。"},"zh-hans":{"1050–":"1050年–殁","1047–1080":"1047年–1080年","1050–Female":"1050年–殁","1052–1096":"1052年–1096年","1045–1086":"1045年–1086年","1070–1130":"1070年–1130年","1072–Female":"1072年–殁","1074–Male":"1074年–殁","1020–1070":"1020年–1070年","1035–1080":"1035年–1080年","about 1072":"大约1072年","1080":"1080年","about 1063":"大约1063年","about 1074":"大约1074年","before 1038":"1038年之前","1066":"1066年","1020":"1020年","1130":"1130年","1086":"1086年","1074":"1074年","1096":"1096年","1052":"1052年","1050":"1050年","1072":"1072年","1070":"1070年","1047":"1047年","1035":"1035年","1045":"1045年","Falaise, Calvados, Normandy, France":"法国諾門迪卡爾瓦多斯法拉","Derbyshire, England":"英国德比夏爾","Europe":"艾歐洛","Salisbury, Wiltshire, England":"英国維爾爾索爾茲伯里","lifeSummary":"当Mathilda de Derbyshire于1050年出生在英国德比夏爾时，她的父亲William F. de Derbyshire31岁，母亲Lady P De Normandie15岁。她于大约1063年与Ranulph Fitz-Hubert de Rie在法国諾門迪卡爾瓦多斯法拉结婚。他们至少是1个儿子和2个女儿的父母。她去世在英国維爾爾索爾茲伯里。"},"hr":{"1050–":"1050.–preminula","1047–1080":"1047–1080","1050–Female":"1050.–preminula","1052–1096":"1052–1096","1045–1086":"1045–1086","1070–1130":"1070.–1130","1072–Female":"1072–preminula","1074–Male":"1074–preminuo","1020–1070":"1020–1070.","1035–1080":"1035–1080","about 1072":"oko 1072.","1080":"1080","about 1063":"oko 1063.","about 1074":"oko 1074.","before 1038":"prije 1038.","1066":"1066","1020":"1020","1130":"1130","1086":"1086","1074":"1074","1096":"1096","1052":"1052","1050":"1050.","1072":"1072","1070":"1070.","1047":"1047","1035":"1035","1045":"1045","Falaise, Calvados, Normandy, France":"Falaise, Calvados, Normandie, Francuska","Derbyshire, England":"Derbyshire, England","Europe":"Europe","Salisbury, Wiltshire, England":"Salisbury, Wiltshire, England"},"cs":{"1050–":"1050–Zesnulá","1047–1080":"1047–1080","10